                <h1>Boost Focus with Brown Noise for ADHD</h1>
                <p>Brown noise has gained attention for its potential benefits in managing ADHD symptoms. Unlike white noise, brown noise offers a deeper sound that can help mask distractions and enhance focus. Many individuals with ADHD find that listening to brown noise while studying or working promotes a sense of calm, allowing for improved concentration and reduced anxiety levels.</p>
